safeguard the authority of the Central Committee and the Central
Military Commission of the Communist Party of China (CPC)
</P>
<P>
The most important point in observing political discipline is
that all actions must follow the demands of the CPC Central
Committee and the Central Military Commission, said Fu Quanyou,
chief of the general staff of the Chinese People's Liberation Army
(PLA).
</P>
<P>
