General Staff should play an exemplary role for all military
organs and troops in firmly following the CPC's absolute
leadership over the army, he said.
</P>
<P>
In particular, he urged senior and middle-level military
officers to abide by the fundamental political norms of the Party
so as to ensure the smooth implementation of administrative and
military directives.
</P>
