<HEADLINE> "Guarantee Quality of Means of Agricultural Production" </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 26 (Xinhua) -- Chinese departments in charge
of commodity circulation and quality control have been urged to
keep an open eye on the quality of means of agricultural
production before this year's spring plowing.
</P>
<P>
"The quality of means of agricultural production for growing
major crops in key areas must be guaranteed in order to ensure a
bumper harvest this year," State Councillor Chen Junsheng said
here today.
</P>
<P>
A key measure is to clear poor-quality products, such as fake
and shoddy seeds, fertilizers and pesticides, out of commodity
circulation, Chen told a national telephone conference.
</P>
<P>
The state-owned distributors and supply and marketing
cooperatives in the rural areas should continue to play a leading
role in distributing seeds, chemical fertilizers and other
materials, he said.
</P>
<P>
Local departments concerned should launch successive checks in
enterprises producing and selling means of agricultural
production. Local governments must strengthen crackdowns upon the
production and sale of fake seeds, chemical fertilizers and
pesticides, which may cause heavy economic losses for farmers, he
urged.
</P>
<P>
He also suggested that agrotechnicians should help farmers
learn how to buy genuine and quality means of agricultural
production. 
</P>
</TEXT>
