<HEADLINE> Senior Official Calls for Study of Military Theory, Science </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 26 (Xinhua) -- A senior military official has
urged all the officers and men of the People's Liberation Army
(PLA) to arm themselves with correct military theory and modern
military science and technology.
</P>
<P>
The two aspects, which have been much emphasized by Chinese
President Jiang Zemin, are keys to building a powerful army, said
Yu Yongbo, member of the Central Military Commission (CMC) and
director of the General Political Department of the PLA.
</P>
<P>
Correct military theory means that the people's army should
obey the Communist Party's absolute leadership and unswervingly
keep in line with the Central Committee with Jiang at the core and
the CMC of the Communist Party of China (CPC), Yu said.
</P>
<P>
At the same time, high technology has become a basic factor in
raising the army's combat effectiveness, he said.
</P>
<P>
Fu made the remarks at a recent conference in which some
military units and individuals talked about their experiences in
stepping up theoretical studies and in the application of modern
military science.
</P>
<P>
The entire PLA must take the study of military theory and
science as a major political task, Fu stressed. 
</P>
