<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 26 (Xinhua) -- The General Political
Department of the Chinese People's Liberation Army (PLA) released
a circular here today requiring all troops and armed police to
study President Jiang Zemin's memorial speech for Deng Xiaoping.
</P>
<P>
Such study is of great significance for remembering the
remarkable deeds and great ideological contributions of Deng
Xiaoping, and for uniting closer around the Central Committee and
the Central Military Commission of the Communist Party of China
