organize officers and men to study other memorial documents,
articles and video materials.
</P>
<P>
Through the study, all troops and armed police should make
efforts to safeguard the authority of the third generation of the
collective leadership of the CPC Central Committee with Jiang
Zemin at the core, according to the circular. 
