event when the deputies, representing the interests of all the
Chinese people, exercise their democratic rights in deciding
important issues of the state.
</P>
<P>
Many deputies said that, with their broad-ranged inspections
and soliciting of opinions and proposals from the public, they are
fully prepared for the upcoming session.
</P>
