<HEADLINE> HK Graduates to Have Mainland Internship Experience </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, February 27 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese University of
Hong Kong has launched a large-scale internship program on the
Chinese mainland to equip students with increasingly valuable
mainland work experience, according to today's South China Morning
Post.
</P>
<P>
