The scheme was recommended by the university's highest advisory
body to address the challenges after the handover, according to
the report.
</P>
<P>
A professor with the university said that it's important for
Hong Kong to put itself in a position conducive to a better
understanding of the systems and intricacies of work in China. The
internship awards provide a golden opportunity for the graduates
to rectify misconceptions and at the same time gain valuable
experience.  
