Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN), its trade will
become freer and wider.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at the inauguration of Myanmar Trade Fair '97, the
minister said that Myanmar, which enjoys observer status in the
ASEAN Economic Group and is a founding member of the World Trade
Organization, sincerely hopes to become a member of the ASEAN in
the near future.
</P>
