temporally for security reasons.
</P>
<P>
Amama Mbabazi, State Minister of Defense, said that the Gulu
Airport could be a possible target of the Sudanese air forces,
referring to earlier air raids by Sudanese aircrafts on
northwestern cities of Moyo and Arua on February 13.
</P>
