<HEADLINE> China's Top Advisory Body Opens Annual Session (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 27 (Xinhua) -- The Fifth Session of the
National Committee of Eighth Chinese People's Political
Consultative Conference (CPPCC), China's top advisory body, opened
here today.
</P>
<P>
This is the last session of China's broadest patriotic united
front organization.
</P>
<P>
Li Ruihuan, chairman of the Eighth CPPCC National Committee,
presided over today's meeting.
</P>
<P>
Jiang Zemin, Li Peng, Qiao Shi, Zhu Rongji, Liu Huaqing, Hu
Jintao and Rong Yiren, and other Party and government leaders
attended the meeting.
</P>
<P>
Today, the Great Hall of the People was filled with
representatives from various parties, people's organizations,
figures without any party affiliation, compatriots from Taiwan,
Hong Kong and Taiwan, and representatives of different ethnic
groups in China.
</P>
<P>
Out of a total of 2,081 members of the CPPCC National
Committee, 1,846 attended today's meeting.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970227.0143 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-02-27 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> China's Top Advisory Body Opens Annual Session (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
At 3:00 p.m., Li Ruihuan declared the meeting open. After the
playing of the national anthem, he said, "on the eve of the Fifth
Session of the Eighth CPPCC National Committee, our respected
Comrade Xiaoping passed away."
</P>
<P>
He said,"Comrade Deng Xiaoping was an outstanding leader whose
immense prestige is recognized by the whole Party, the whole army
and people of all ethnic groups throughout the country. He was a
great Marxist, a great statesman, a military strategist and a
diplomat, and a long-tested Communist fighter, the chief architect
of China's socialist reforms, opening-up, and modernization drive,
and the founder of the theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics.
</P>
<P>
"Comrade Deng Xiaoping, who served as chairman of the Fifth
CPPCC National Committee, was the founder of the people's
consultative cause in the new historical period. His important
thinking on the united front and the people's political
consultative conference is an integral part of the theory of
building socialism with Chinese characteristics, and the
scientific guideline for the work of the people's political
consultative conference.
</P>
<P>
"The passing of Comrade Xiaoping was an immeasurable loss to
the Party, the army and people of all ethnic groups throughout
China. We must turn grief into strength, carry forward Comrade
Deng Xiaoping's behest, rally still more closely around the
Central Committee of the Communist Party of China with Comrade
Jiang Zemin at the core, hold high the great banner of Deng
Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics, adhere to the basic line of the Party, and carry
forward the great cause of socialist reform and opening-up and
modernization drive pioneered by Comrade Deng Xiaoping."
</P>
<P>
Then, Li Ruihuan proposed that all present stand up in silent
mourning for Deng Xiaoping.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
