tons of crude oil and bring 600 million cubic meters of associated
gas ashore to meet the demand of the Phu My 2 and Ba Ria power
plants for oil.
</P>
<P>
This company is also preparing for several important projects
including the construction of the country's first oil refinery and
gas pipeline.
</P>
<P>
By the end of January, Petrol Vietnam had signed 32 joint
venture contracts worth more than two billion U.S. dollars
involving the exploration and exploitation of oil and gas. 
