<DOCNO> XIE19970227.0200 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-02-27 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> 11th Panchen Mourns for Deng Xiaoping </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LHASA, February 27 (Xinhua) -- The 11th Panchen Lama, grieved
by the passing of Deng Xiaoping on the morning of February 20,
told the people around him that he was saddened by the loss.
</P>
<P>
Deng's great accomplishments will be remembered forever by the
Tibetan people and the Chinese people from other ethnic groups,
said Panchen Erdeni Qoigyijadu, who was confirmed as the soul boy
for the 10th Panchen Lama by drawing lots from a golden urn in
November, 1995. The State Council approved the reincarnation.
</P>
<P>
Panchen said that to show his respect to the late senior
leader, he will make good use of his time, study hard and become a
living Buddha who pledges his love to his country and Buddhism.
</P>
<P>
He presented a hada to a portrait of Deng Xiaoping. Hada is a
piece of silk used as a greeting gift among the Tibetan and
Mongolian people.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
