companies allegedly involved in laundering drug money are being
investigated by the Federal Attorney-General's Office in Colombia.
</P>
<P>
The companies include two owned by the Rodriguez Orejuela
brothers Gilberto and Miguel, leaders of the Cali cartel, who were
jailed in January.
</P>
<P>
