untouched before talks on a final settlement between the
Palestinian Liberation Organization (PLO) and Israel will start
next month, Muasher said.
</P>
<P>
The minister said that the Jewish settlement in Jerusalem
would pose danger to the peace process after positive results
were achieved towards a comprehensive peace.
</P>
<P>
Israeli cabinet today approved the building of new Jewish
houses in Arab's Jerusalem despite international
opposition. Israeli Prime Minister Binyamin Netanyahu warned the
Palestinians not to respond by violence. 
